knowledgeGraph.title: Canby Family Practice Clinic
knowledgeGraph.description: Canby Family Practice Clinic in Canby, California, United States is a medical and dental clinic. Established in 1987, the clinic moved to its current location in 2001. Medical, dental, behavioral health, and related services are available. Medicaid and Medicare insurances are accepted.
